column2: Arctic lands
as an unplanned distraction
at the feast
at the great feast
at the summer fair
at the festival
dance
It was about various events in our realm that were unusual, to say the least.
It was a long story about a commoner that kept making the wrong choices and who found himself in ridiculous situations.
It was about famous [liege.Religion.GetPriestTitle]s that did ridiculous things.
I almost fell asleep halfway through the story.
The story was confusing and I don't think I understood the jokes.
There were some funny jokes but most of it was boring.
The story was actually interesting and [jester.GetSheHe] made me laugh a few times.
This was one of the best story I have ever heard!
It was a song mocking every lord of our realm.
It was a song about the [random_neighbor_culture.GetName] people.
It was so loud and [jester.GetHerHis] voice was so unpleasant that I wanted to leave.
I didn't even know what the song was about until [jester.GetSheHe] told me at the end, and the melody was... wrong.
I think it was supposed to be funny, but it only got me a small chuckle.
I really liked when [jester.GetSheHe] talked about [jester_flavor_song_target.GetTitledName].
The parodies were completely accurate!
[jester.GetFirstName] played an absurd music with [jester.GetHerHis] lute
[jester.GetFirstName] told a small story accompanied with [jester.GetHerHis] lyre
I don't even know why I was listening for more than ten seconds.
I want to get this out of my head.
I think screams of dying animals are as interesting as this.
The melody reminded me of something amusing that happened.
[jester.GetSheHeCap] even made a silly dance during the performance. What a delight!
It was a parody of another famous poem, with added jokes.
[jester.GetSheHeCap] made a new poem and wanted to recite it for the first time in front of me.
I think I hate poetry, now.
It was boring and uninteresting.
I appreciate the effort, but this did nothing for me.
The verses were actually well thought out.
I haven't laughed like that in a long time, [jester.GetSheHe] even kept the right number of syllables for the whole poem!
Other performers joined [jester.GetHerHim] in a balance performance.
[jester.GetSheHeCap] tried to tame and ride wild animals.
I didn't know one could trip while doing so little.
I don't think falling head-first was part of it.
It resembled cattle bumping into each other.
I liked the shapes they represented.
[jester.GetFirstName] was particularily agile and stable!
[jester.GetSheHeCap] took a few balls made of cloth and made tricks with them.
[jester.GetSheHeCap] juggled quite a few knives. It looked dangerous.
How many times did [jester.GetSheHe] drop those things?
I think [jester.GetSheHe] managed to keep two of them in the air... sometimes.
But what was the point of this?
Some of those tricks were quite interesting. I liked this show.
The way [jester.GetSheHe] threw them! Impressive!
Those jokes were mostly about noblemen of our realm.
The jokes were mocking famous people of our time.
Did [jester.GetSheHe] call me a [Getjester.GetFromRootInsult]?
It was enjoyable until [jester.GetSheHe] brought up [diplomatic_target.GetTitledName]. [diplomatic_target.GetSheHeCap] should not be disrespected like that.
It wasn't good, but at least it wasn't insulting.
The one about [diplomatic_target.GetTitledName] was so accurate!
I still get a laugh jester.those jokes now!
[jester.GetSheHeCap] made different items disappear in front of the public.
[jester.GetSheHeCap] made sleight-of-hand tricks with ropes and coins.
I could see the trick everytime...
Next time [jester.GetSheHe] shouldn't drop everything when bowing.
[jester.GetSheHeCap] tried, but it wasn't interesting.
I liked the way [jester.GetSheHe] made those tricks.
How is this possible? [jester.GetSheHeCap] did that perfectly!
[jester.GetFirstName] started meowing on all fours and walking delicately
Get this mad [jester.GetManWoman] out of here.
I can't stop yawning
Hmm...
Why am I laughing at this?
Meow!
